The main library package; contains several sub-packages and miscellaneous classes

Classes to easily "activate" and "deactivate" servos, continuous rotation servos, and DC motors

ErrorTimeThresholdFinishingAlgorithm - Class in edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller
Uses error tolerance and time threshold to determine when to stop running the controller and count it as "finished." The robot must stay within the error tolerance continuously for the time given in the time threshold to finish.
